					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13436796#post-4691566</guid>
				<title>Author post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13436796/scp-5081#post-4691566</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2020 21:18:41 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Attila the Pun</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1685633</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>A format screw, by someone who hates format screws.</p> <p>This CorpseCon entry was a tough one to write. The conprocs pushed the article hard into a writing style I'm not comfortable with <em>at all</em>.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marcelles-raynes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5722579&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592523447" alt="Marcelles_Raynes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5722579)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marcelles-raynes" >Marcelles_Raynes</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592523447" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguepjp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5813664&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592523447" alt="PlaguePJP" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5813664)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguepjp" >PlaguePJP</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592523447" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tyumen" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2951719&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592523447" alt="Tyumen" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2951719)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tyumen" >Tyumen</a></span> and others for crit!</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Some&nbsp;extra&nbsp;notes</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Some&nbsp;extra&nbsp;notes</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>For the court summons at the end, I used two official court summons as a template: one from the <a href="https://www.uscourts.gov/forms/notice-lawsuit-summons-subpoena/summons-civil-action">US District Court system</a>, and one from the state of New York. Both of these documents are public domain, and I believe that I have modified it enough that what is in the article is distinct from either source; however, something may have slipped through the cracks and I would like this on record in case it comes up.</p> <p>Also, because I know <em>somebody</em> will probably bring it up, the 555 number does not exist as that area code is reserved. It's actually a fairly common practice to give a fictional number that area code so nobody gets called by curious readers.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
